{"tid":1793461,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] TVB《台灣原味道》有死曼狗梁凱晴！！","createTime":"2019-12-22T12:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T13:10:10.000Z","uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e2f00c8deecacd9d5ded3145910ade33314cfb3c","tid":1793461,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:04:19.000Z","msg":"譚玉瑛帶領區永權、孔德賢，聯同台灣土生土長的梁凱晴，開展寶島原味道之行。台灣人重視養生，當地有雞場採用「友善畜牧」，雞隻竟是吃中藥長大？雞場出產的雞蛋有「六星級雞蛋」的美譽，阿譚放心將三層雞蛋滑進嘴裡！<br />\n<br />\n養生美食還有甕仔雞，甕仔烤焗，原汁原味。又跟養生達人參觀熬雞精工場， 雞隻經八小時熬製出濃縮精華，是補身佳品。主持們走到紅樹林下，隨「馬蹄蛤之父」挖掘營養豐富的馬蹄蛤，肉質軟滑之餘，蛤殼亦有功用。"},{"pid":"d95e79be65d9068e67d024c23ae88afd2f7565fc","tid":1793461,"uid":311583,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:04:34.000Z","msg":"【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【置頂】【行動po求推】好㷫呀！警曱向人群舉槍，聽日同我即刻行動。而嚟緊嘅行動係1223stuck稅局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793389</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WvBryAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvBryAY.jpg&h=fea3e57a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddDxvuv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddDxvuv.jpg&h=525dd049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai